  <brief_title>Comparison of Self-assessment vs. Assessment by Others of Critically Ill Patients</brief_title>
  <acronym>ASTON</acronym>
  <official_title>Agreement in Relatives' Assessment in Standardized Questionnaires of Patients Who Have Been Admitted to Intensive Care Compared to Patients Who Have Not Been Admitted to Intensive Care (ASTON Study)</official_title>
