  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We will test the results of standardized questionnaires for patients admitted to intensive
      care assessed by relatives/caregivers compared to the patient itself. Furthermore we will
      compare results with patients not admitted to intensive care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
